title: Reptar!
description: Just when you thought it was safe to visit New York, here comes Reptar! He’s big, he’s green, he’s mean, and he’s back! This time, he means business!
altHero: Reptar, a giant t-rex, stomps through the city
alt1: Reptar chomps on a chunk of building
alt2: Reptar destroys a building with his tail
alt3: Reptar breathes fire at an airplane
alt4: Reptar grabs another giant dinosaur by the neck
